{"tid":1350671,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"著名排球評述員雷禮義逝世　終年71歲","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T14:56:21.000Z","uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ed10b5a51d1b3caa806cfcea96b8b2bc8fa1c1ec","tid":1350671,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:27:50.000Z","msg":"2019-07-22 HKT 21:23<br />\n <br />\n本港著名排球評述員雷禮義逝世，終年71歲。<br />\n<br />\n雷禮義是本港第一位國際排球裁判，他經常在評述賽事時，以「食叉燒」來形容輕鬆扣剎得分，最為觀眾熟悉。<br />\n<br />\n多名體育界人士在網上發文悼念。他的家人表示，雷禮義希望低調處理後事，火化後才公布死訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469835-20190722.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469835-20190722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=7a838dc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469835-20190722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f4a27018\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469835-20190722.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n雷蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食叉燒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fc66b6c0806eb705b15e6f8ad25f535d5e04f0","tid":1350671,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc3d7eda096e12ef7c4ff83cf4fb9cd13401a30","tid":1350671,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雷sir<br />\n但發生咁多野唔知仲有無人理"},{"pid":"859bd80c5a0c281883745acaee587ff95ad9600c","tid":1350671,"uid":19847,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"以前睇奧運好鍾意聽佢講食叉燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr